# Xcode
build/
DerivedData/
*.xcodeproj/xcuserdata/
*.xcodeproj/project.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/
*.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.moved-aside
*.pbxuser
!default.pbxuser
*.mode1v3
!default.mode1v3
*.mode2v3
